data.description: Gorgeous and spacious home with solar panels on an oversized corner lot on a greenbelt! This 2 story home features 2 living areas,  2 and 1/2 bathrooms, 5 bedrooms, a beautiful eat in kitchen with granite counter tops, a double car garage, and an upstairs utility room. The downstairs area consists of a half bathroom, open living room and kitchen, and the primary bedroom with ensuite. The upstairs area features a large game room with four generously sized bedrooms along with a full bathroom. Enjoy the energy savings with your solar panels - electric bills average $35/month! This home is a must see in a beautifully planned subdivision with a neighborhood park across the street.
